==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: sān rì bù dúshū, miànmùkĕzēng

===Etymology===
Literally: If you don't read for three days, you will become unattractive.

===Proverb===
'''[[三]][[日]][[不]][[读书]]，[[面目可憎]]'''

# If you are not diligent in your studies, you will remain ignorant, and nobody will be attracted to you.

===Alternate forms===
[[三日不讀書，面目可憎]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

